title: UDEMY LEARN 20 POWERFUL HYPNOTIC WORDS FOR INFLUENCE AND PERSUAS
description:
UDEMY LEARN 20 POWERFUL HYPNOTIC WORDS FOR INFLUENCE AND PERSUASION TUTORIAL


What are the requirements?

* PC with high speed internet
* Quiet room
* Headphones
* High focus and concentration
* Notebook and pen

What am I going to get from this course?

* Over 12 lectures and 40 mins of content!
* By the end of this course you will master conversational hypnosis techniques and learn 20 powerful words that can be used for persuasion and influencing people
* You will be more confident and achieve more success while conversing with people and will be able to influence them more effectively than before and achieve your goals
* You will be more conscious of the words you use in your daily life and have a positive impact

What is the target audience?

* This course is for everyone who are into sales, marketing, soft skills trainers , stage performers etc who require lot of influencing and convincing people in their daily life
* Age group 16 and above
